from college scouts

28:48.435 --> 28:50.103
when you were coming out of high school?

30:33.790 --> 30:37.252
What do you remember
about that day in 1984?

38:08.160 --> 38:10.788
It's bigger than just being
knocked out of the playoffs.

38:10.871 --> 38:12.957
It's the end of an era.

41:00.458 --> 41:03.043
Yeah. The chemo, I can't hear real well,
so you gotta...

41:56.805 --> 41:58.140
