42:25.125 --> 42:26.794
Some can, some can't?

42:27.461 --> 42:29.213
Some can, some can't.

42:31.715 --> 42:33.384
That's just the way it is.

42:35.135 --> 42:37.888
-You stay away from Scott Burrell.
-I...

